<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Luis Feliz Caballero — Mentoría Privada Forex</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=IM+Fell+English:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@latest/tabler-icons.min.css" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    :root {
      --gold: #C8A96E;
      --gold-dim: #8a7040;
      --gold-bg: #0d0b08;
      --gold-border: #2a1f0f;
      --black: #0A0A0A;
      --black-2: #060606;
      --text-primary: #F0EDE6;
      --text-secondary: #E0DDD6;
      --text-muted: #888;
      --text-dim: #666;
      --text-ghost: #444;
      --text-dead: #333;
      --border: #1e1e1e;
      --border-dark: #141414;
      --border-darker: #1a1a1a;
      --red-dim: #5a2020;
      --red-dead: #4a3535;
      --red-ghost: #3a1515;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--black);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ── UTILITIES ── */
    .inner {
      max-width: 1040px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 4rem;
    }

    .label-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }
    .label-line {
      height: 0.5px;
      width: 28px;
      background: var(--gold);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .label-text {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .section-divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
    }

    .cta-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--black);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 1rem 2.8rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: opacity 0.18s;
    }
    .cta-primary:hover { opacity: 0.82; }

    .cta-ghost {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-ghost);
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-decoration-color: var(--border);
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .cta-ghost:hover { color: var(--text-muted); }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.4rem 4rem;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid #1a1a1a;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: var(--black);
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .nav-cta {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--gold);
      padding: 0.55rem 1.4rem;
      transition: background 0.18s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.08); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 7rem 0 6rem;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-ghost);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .hero-h1 {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.08;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      max-width: 700px;
    }
    .hero-h1 em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 560px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }
    .hero-filter {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--text-ghost);
      border-left: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* ── AGITATION ── */
    .agitation {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
    }
    .agitation-h2 {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 640px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .agitation-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-ghost);
      max-width: 500px;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .agitation-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .agitation-cell {
      padding: 2.25rem 2rem;
      border-right: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .agitation-cell:nth-child(2n) { border-right: none; }
    .agitation-cell:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: none; }
    .cell-num {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--text-dead);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .cell-title {
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }
    .cell-body {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .agitation-quote {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 640px;
    }
    .agitation-quote strong {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    /* ── PARADIGM ── */
    .paradigm {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
    }
    .paradigm-h2 {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 580px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .paradigm-intro {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      max-width: 600px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .paradigm-cols {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border-darker);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .paradigm-col {
      background: var(--black);
      padding: 2.25rem 2rem;
    }
    .col-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .col-old .col-label { color: #4a2211; }
    .col-new .col-label { color: var(--gold); }
    .paradigm-list {
      list-style: none;
    }
    .paradigm-list li {
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 0.7rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-dark);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .paradigm-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .col-old .paradigm-list li { color: #4a3535; }
    .col-new .paradigm-list li { color: #A8A49C; }
    .paradigm-statement {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--gold);
      line-height: 1.85;
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--gold-border);
      background: var(--gold-bg);
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    /* ── MECHANISM ── */
    .mechanism {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
      background: var(--black-2);
    }
    .mechanism-h2 {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 560px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .mechanism-intro {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      max-width: 540px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .mechanism-layers {
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .layer {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-dark);
    }
    .layer:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .layer-label {
      padding: 2rem;
      border-right: 0.5px solid var(--border-dark);
    }
    .layer-roman {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--gold-dim);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }
    .layer-name {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .layer-body {
      padding: 2rem;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    /* ── AUTHORITY ── */
    .authority {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
    }
    .authority-h2 {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 620px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .authority-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .authority-aside {
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem;
      position: sticky;
      top: 74px;
    }
    .aside-name {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: 1.55rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }
    .aside-role {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dead);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .aside-stat {
      padding: 0.9rem 0;
      border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
    }
    .stat-num {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-ghost);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .authority-body p {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #777;
      line-height: 1.85;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .authority-body p strong {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Prueba Verificable */
    .proof-box {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--gold-border);
      background: var(--gold-bg);
    }
    .proof-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold-dim);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .proof-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #7a6a50;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .proof-text strong { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; }

    /* ── DELIVERABLES ── */
    .deliverables {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
      background: var(--black-2);
    }
    .deliverables-h2 {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 560px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .deliverables-sub {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-ghost);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .deliverables-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border-darker);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .deliverable-item {
      background: var(--black-2);
      padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    }
    .d-title {
      display: block;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .d-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .not-included {
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--black);
    }
    .not-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--red-dim);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .not-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem 2rem;
    }
    .not-list li {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--red-dead);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
    }
    .not-list li i { font-size: 13px; color: var(--red-ghost); }

    /* ── FILTER ── */
    .filter {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
    }
    .filter-h2 {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 560px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .filter-cols {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .filter-col {
      padding: 2rem;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .filter-col-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .filter-col-not .filter-col-label { color: var(--red-dim); }
    .filter-col-yes .filter-col-label { color: var(--gold); }
    .filter-list {
      list-style: none;
    }
    .filter-list li {
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 0.7rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-dark);
      line-height: 1.55;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .filter-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .filter-col-not .filter-list li { color: var(--red-dead); }
    .filter-col-yes .filter-list li { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .icon-no { color: var(--red-ghost); font-size: 15px; min-width: 15px; margin-top: 1px; }
    .icon-yes { color: var(--gold); font-size: 15px; min-width: 15px; margin-top: 1px; }

    /* ── TRUTH BOX ── */
    .truth {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-darker);
      background: var(--black-2);
    }
    .truth-h2 {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 480px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .truth-items {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      max-width: 680px;
    }
    .truth-item {
      padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-dark);
    }
    .truth-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .truth-item-title {
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }
    .truth-item-body {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .truth-close {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--gold-dim);
      font-style: italic;
      border-left: 1px solid var(--gold-border);
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
      max-width: 520px;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    /* ── FINAL CTA ── */
    .final-cta {
      padding: 8rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .final-pre {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-ghost);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .final-h2 {
      font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .final-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-ghost);
      max-width: 440px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .final-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .final-note {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-dead);
      max-width: 400px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    .footer {
      padding: 2rem 4rem;
      border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border-dark);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .footer-copy {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-dead);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }
    .footer-legal {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #2a2a2a;
      max-width: 400px;
      text-align: right;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .inner { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
      .nav { padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; }
      .hero { padding: 4rem 0 3.5rem; }
      .agitation-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .agitation-cell { border-right: none !important; }
      .agitation-cell:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
      .agitation-cell:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      .paradigm-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .layer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .layer-label { border-right: none; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-dark); }
      .authority-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .authority-aside { position: static; }
      .deliverables-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .filter-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
      .footer-legal { text-align: center; }
      .final-cta { padding: 5rem 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav">
  <span class="nav-logo">Luis Feliz Caballero</span>
  <a class="nav-cta" href="#apply">Solicitar Acceso</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Mentoría Privada · Forex · Plazas Limitadas</p>
    <h1 class="hero-h1">
      Tienes el capital.<br>
      <em>Te falta el marco operativo.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Luis enseña el mismo marco con el que opera: lectura de mercado, entradas, gestión de riesgo y control emocional. Es entrenamiento puro para tomar decisiones con capital real. Sin atajos. Sin señales. Sin promesas de ingresos pasivos.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-filter">
      Si buscas un sistema que opere por ti mientras descansas, esta página no es para ti. Si buscas la habilidad para operar tú mismo con disciplina y criterio — sigue leyendo.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="cta-primary" href="#apply">Ver la presentación</a>
      <button class="cta-ghost" onclick="document.getElementById('about').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Quién es Luis →</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- AGITATION -->
<section class="agitation">
